Guards are cave goblins guards found in Dorgesh-Kaan, guarding the entrance to the city and wandering around the city.

If a player fails to pickpocket a Dorgeshuun citizen, a nearby guard will occasionally say "Stop that!" and attack.

They can be of some profit to players as their drops can be sold to the nearby Dorgeshuun store. These goblins can only be accessed after completing the Lost Tribe quest.
